     mmoopphheerrccttll controls the mopher daemon.

     Available options are:

     --hh      Show usage message.

     --dd _l_e_v_e_l
             Set logging severity level to _l_e_v_e_l

     --cc _f_i_l_e
             Read configuration from _f_i_l_e.

     --ss _h_o_s_t
             Connect to _h_o_s_t.

     _c_o_m_m_a_n_d is one of the following:

     dump _t_a_b_l_e
             Print raw content of _t_a_b_l_e.

     greylist dump
             Print formatted content of the greylist-table.

     greylist pass _o_r_i_g_i_n _f_r_o_m _r_c_p_t
             Temporarily whitelist triplet.

